{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vaporware Odyssey is a action roguelike inspired by vaporwave and synthwave aesthetics. It blends souls-like and bullet hell mechanics to create a uniquely action packed experience.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25c6 <strong>Procedurally generated levels</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Every room in the game is procedurally generated on a hex grid.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089540/extras/Grid.png?t=1733430576\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25c6\u00a0 <strong>Synergetic Upgrades</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Most upgrades are designed to synergies in fun and useful ways. There is almost always more then one way to combine upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089540/extras/Poison_Upgrade.png?t=1733430576\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089540/extras/Ring_Of_Fire_Upgrade.png?t=1733430576\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089540/extras/Alure_Upgrade.png?t=1733430576\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u25c6 Intense combat focused on <strong>dodging and jumping</strong> to avoid enemy attacks. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3089540/extras/Dodge.png?t=1733430576\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com